Ascension Funnel
To turn a casual visitor into a Sovereign Contributor, we use the “Ascension Funnel“.
This is not a sales funnel; it is a gamified path toward Digital and Structural Sovereignty.
Visitors earn Experience Points (XP) which translate into influence within the Equity Index 2.0.

