The Ascension Funnel: From Visitor to Guardian

The Ascension Funnel: From Visitor to Guardian
Level	Stage	Tasks (XP Rewards)	Outcome
0	The Observer	Visit the Landing Platform; Read the “Green Renaissance” Thesis (10 XP)	Awareness of the Mission
1	The Citizen	Claim your Virtual Identity; Sign the “Declaration of Global Hemp Sovereignty” (50 XP)	Digital Onboarding
2	The Node	Install a basic “Software Node” on your device; Join the HempNet Commons (150 XP)	Connectivity
3	The Eco-Guardian	Activate a physical sensor (soil/air) or host a Cooperative Server (500 XP)	Real-time Data Contribution
4	The Architect	Submit a 3D-printing design to the Developer Hub; Lead a Buddytask (1000 XP)	Structural Production
5	The Sovereign	Become a Verified Validator on the Global Hemp Ledger (5000 XP)	Network Governance
